<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">Processes other than fire primarily disturb stands. They include salt spray, yearly variation in moisture, wind-blown sand accretion, and sand/bluff erosion.</div>
